(1+\cos \theta + i \sin \theta)^n + (1+\cos \theta - i \sin \theta)^n=2^{n+1}\cos^n\frac{\theta}{2}\cos\frac{n\theta}{2}
e^{i\theta}
\sin^2\theta + \cos^2\theta=(\cos\theta+i\sin\theta)(\cos\theta-i\sin\theta)
1+\cos2x=2\sin^2x
\sin2x=2\sin x\cos x
(1+\cos x + i\sin x)^n =(2\cos^2 x+i(2\sin\frac{x}{2}\cos\frac{x}{2}))^n
=[2\cos \frac{x}{2} (cos\frac{x}{2} + i\sin \frac {x}{2})]^n
=2^n \cos^n \frac{x}{2} (\cos \frac{nx}{2} + i \sin \frac{nx}{2})
